text: Stuart Young-Black (born 21 July 1959) is a Canadian equestrian. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Canada Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1987 Pan American Games Category:Pan American Games medalists in equestrian Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Canada Category:Sportspeople from Macclesfield
